{"tid":106850,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲去過烏克蘭?想請教","createTime":"2017-02-04T04:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T10:34:27.000Z","uid":75637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"498d13e2494bfc1f5ca91b5de504624bb4f7c8fb","tid":106850,"uid":75637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T04:21:42.000Z","msg":"大家好，想請教吓各位巴絲，因為俄航優惠，買左去波蘭機票，黎緊6月會去。而烏克蘭喺波蘭隔離，都會順便去埋。我暫時plan左stay烏克蘭 9日。<br />\n行程如下:<br />\nday 1-2: lviv<br />\nday 3-5: odessa<br />\nday6-9 : kiev +chernobyl<br />\n<br />\nlviv 主要四圍行吓無特定景點去，odessa就想去黑海沙灘，kiev就睇吓教堂同前蘇聯地方，chernobyl就join 1day tour.  <br />\n<br />\n有冇去過嘅巴絲分享吓烏克蘭有咩地方景點必去? 同埋上面d城市日數會5會太少/太多?<br />\n<br />\n感謝各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b9906efa9e39ea040885ea4ac352a953582f86","tid":106850,"uid":2171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T04:37:55.000Z","msg":"上年9月去過livi 同keiv , 烏克蘭真心正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff7e751fd9a65d3f9f24d4a7ba308d403140f1b","tid":106850,"uid":2171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T04:38:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上年9月去過Lviv 同keiv , 烏克蘭真心正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f319835780c7e11d2314f03b21c058b93d252a83","tid":106850,"uid":75637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上年9月去過Lviv 同keiv , 烏克蘭真心正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你 lviv留左幾多日?<br />\n<br />\n同埋想問你有冇買電話卡? 我見烏克蘭d上網好多都係得3G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知買邊間d電話卡好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f70dfd68a8163cfd69ad6b21b2f42861a5185b","tid":106850,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:30:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上年9月去過Lviv 同keiv , 烏克蘭真心正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你 lviv留左幾多日?<br />\n<br />\n同埋想問你有冇買電話卡? 我見烏克蘭d上網好多都係得3G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知買邊間d電話卡好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMTS UA ，用佢個 3G 都 OK 唔慢<br />\n<br />\n另外你回程係點走？<br />\n<br />\n都係波蘭返莫斯科走？<br />\n<br />\n你去到 Odessa 點走要諗埋。<br />\n<br />\n你去完波蘭後，再去 Lviv 會覺得差唔多。<br />\n<br />\nKyiv 要睇都有唔少景點睇，睇自己興趣。<br />\n<br />\nOdessa 我都係去睇黑海日出日落，另外有個大城堡幾大下，但太遠我都冇去到。"},{"pid":"f8f68352983be4818b422e3e6296bf8dc8f4d565","tid":106850,"uid":53981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:54:41.000Z","msg":"淨係去過Kiev 同Chernobyl, 都係夾埋四日，個人覺得夠<br />\n利申 旅行好hea"},{"pid":"233b01ac50eb53495f9a4a4bcdf4d5cc47797b69","tid":106850,"uid":75637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T06:05:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上年9月去過Lviv 同keiv , 烏克蘭真心正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你 lviv留左幾多日?<br />\n<br />\n同埋想問你有冇買電話卡? 我見烏克蘭d上網好多都係得3G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知買邊間d電話卡好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMTS UA ，用佢個 3G 都 OK 唔慢<br />\n<br />\n另外你回程係點走？<br />\n<br />\n都係波蘭返莫斯科走？<br />\n<br />\n你去到 Odessa 點走要諗埋。<br />\n<br />\n你去完波蘭後，再去 Lviv 會覺得差唔多。<br />\n<br />\nKyiv 要睇都有唔少景點睇，睇自己興趣。<br />\n<br />\nOdessa 我都係去睇黑海日出日落，另外有個大城堡幾大下，但太遠我都冇去到。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nthanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初步諗住：香港--＞warsaw--＞krakow (3日）--＞lviv(2日）--＞odessa(3日）--＞kiev+chernobyl(4日）--＞warsaw(2日）--＞香港<br />\n<br />\nkiev 返warsaw會搭飛機，其他城市transit就過夜巴同火車<br />\n<br />\n咁樣順唔順路?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308debba28c9bca96b2b88583c87b8744120a9b2","tid":106850,"uid":75637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T06:07:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係去過Kiev 同Chernobyl, 都係夾埋四日，個人覺得夠<br />\n利申 旅行好hea</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都算hea hea 地咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c5919753bf5bf0d7057b842a0f207f09b92142","tid":106850,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T06:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\nthanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初步諗住：香港--＞warsaw--＞krakow (3日）--＞lviv(2日）--＞odessa(3日）--＞kiev+chernobyl(4日）--＞warsaw(2日）--＞香港<br />\n<br />\nkiev 返warsaw會搭飛機，其他城市transit就過夜巴同火車<br />\n<br />\n咁樣順唔順路?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點會順路呀？<br />\n<br />\nLviv 去 Odessa 坐火車都係要經基輔喎。<br />\n<br />\n尾站應該諗 Odessa<br />\n<br />\n諗由 Odessa 直接飛番華沙，不過就幾貴下。<br />\n<br />\n另一選擇落摩爾多瓦，由 Chisinau 直飛返華沙，但都唔算最平。<br />\n<br />\n再唔係 Odessa 坐 UIA 經基輔飛華沙，都係六百蚊港紙左右。<br />\n<br />\n最短時間可以4個鐘去到華沙。"},{"pid":"e84dfcb647a5a30ce1a3b7491dd01e9198304ead","tid":106850,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T06:51:15.000Z","msg":"電話卡個到，我開左張Vodafone<br />\n勁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你要去佢地門市開，<br />\n佢地會用用極有限英文幫你整"},{"pid":"63df42f4b59a8092c8b5e1d9f46165f3e0e107b2","tid":106850,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T07:24:19.000Z","msg":"唔知樓主坐幾點車由 Krak&oacute;w 坐車落 Lviv，我上年坐夜晚差唔多十點車過去，去到果邊差唔多5-6點。<br />\n<br />\n在火車站/長途車站等找換店開換錢，<br />\n<br />\n喺長途車站售票處座樓側邊有個小窗係找換店，喺果度換錢兼買電話卡。<br />\n<br />\n找換店個RATE同市區內差唔多，我之後都換唔到一間高過佢。<br />\n<br />\n買張卡連埋充咗40 UAH，大約75UAH，夠用到我走為止，老實講唔知有幾多Data，最後果40 UAH 面值，仲可以養住張卡幾個月。(張卡到依家我仲未停，不停入錢養住)"},{"pid":"e57cac74b26e24e9e0a520945fc07e97b82b8bcb","tid":106850,"uid":75637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T07:47:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nthanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初步諗住：香港--＞warsaw--＞krakow (3日）--＞lviv(2日）--＞odessa(3日）--＞kiev+chernobyl(4日）--＞warsaw(2日）--＞香港<br />\n<br />\nkiev 返warsaw會搭飛機，其他城市transit就過夜巴同火車<br />\n<br />\n咁樣順唔順路?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點會順路呀？<br />\n<br />\nLviv 去 Odessa 坐火車都係要經基輔喎。<br />\n<br />\n尾站應該諗 Odessa<br />\n<br />\n諗由 Odessa 直接飛番華沙，不過就幾貴下。<br />\n<br />\n另一選擇落摩爾多瓦，由 Chisinau 直飛返華沙，但都唔算最平。<br />\n<br />\n再唔係 Odessa 坐 UIA 經基輔飛華沙，都係六百蚊港紙左右。<br />\n<br />\n最短時間可以4個鐘去到華沙。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ni see...<br />\n咁唯有lviv  --&gt; kiev --&gt; odessa--&gt; warsaw<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5273dadb612f9e8e0c4e26be47178a92784bd108","tid":106850,"uid":75637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T07:48:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電話卡個到，我開左張Vodafone<br />\n勁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你要去佢地門市開，<br />\n佢地會用用極有限英文幫你整</blockquote><br />\n到時搵吓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfcc56af067cae4ed8b670bce1bb5299fe5717e8","tid":106850,"uid":66130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T07:50:07.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"534d8be798e41bf19223e7c85626c5883a85ce61","tid":106850,"uid":2171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T07:56:08.000Z","msg":"電話卡我係機場買，用kyiv star"},{"pid":"ea9c42e64b7e052a1c7f16a36d5a0e15e50efef9","tid":106850,"uid":75637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:32:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知樓主坐幾點車由 Krak&oacute;w 坐車落 Lviv，我上年坐夜晚差唔多十點車過去，去到果邊差唔多5-6點。<br />\n<br />\n在火車站/長途車站等找換店開換錢，<br />\n<br />\n喺長途車站售票處座樓側邊有個小窗係找換店，喺果度換錢兼買電話卡。<br />\n<br />\n找換店個RATE同市區內差唔多，我之後都換唔到一間高過佢。<br />\n<br />\n買張卡連埋充咗40 UAH，大約75UAH，夠用到我走為止，老實講唔知有幾多Data，最後果40 UAH 面值，仲可以養住張卡幾個月。(張卡到依家我仲未停，不停入錢養住)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我應該會搭polskibus由krakow 去lviv, 夜晚7半開車，第二朝4點幾到lviv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05c111bce7a80a2f78d7265047dc7d9d000aba5","tid":106850,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:46:17.000Z","msg":"留名 想去"},{"pid":"00a2b9117a7e30229c18e94d903288708bc08b0e","tid":106850,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:25:04.000Z","msg":"唔知關唔關個台事，買咗4g但最多只係3g好慢, 出咗大城市成日收唔到tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nkiev可以參加free walking tour (通常完咗會比小費)<br />\nkiev, lviv, odessa 都有劇院，可以睇返場表演，好平 (唔可以著牛仔褲同波鞋)<br />\n食野超抵，唔洗慳，上tripadvisor搵餐廳<br />\nchernobyl tour竟然星期六日平過1-5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nkiev &gt; lviv中途可以去tunnel of love"},{"pid":"973b80911cdd718e658fb4d9391ed8ebcf174124","tid":106850,"uid":75637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T04:56:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知關唔關個台事，買咗4g但最多只係3g好慢, 出咗大城市成日收唔到tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nkiev可以參加free walking tour (通常完咗會比小費)<br />\nkiev, lviv, odessa 都有劇院，可以睇返場表演，好平 (唔可以著牛仔褲同波鞋)<br />\n食野超抵，唔洗慳，上tripadvisor搵餐廳<br />\nchernobyl tour竟然星期六日平過1-5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nkiev &gt; lviv中途可以去tunnel of love</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nthanks<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁我如果4g 價錢同3g 差唔遠都照買既<br />\n<br />\nfree walking tour 會join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽吓當地guide講野認識多d烏克蘭<br />\n<br />\ntunnel of love 要諗吓先，每日好少火車去佢個城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a77402036741127032e5a9aa77f9010253d44d56","tid":106850,"uid":75637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:34:27.000Z","msg":"btw, 有冇巴絲join 過波蘭既free walking tour? 值唔值得join?"}]}